  "texts": [
    "The feature extraction procedure was carried out by converting RGB images to greyscale to decrease computing costs.",
    "Edge filters such as Canny, Roberts, Sobel, Scharr, and Prewitt were utilised for the edge-based features.",
    "Noise and blur were removed using the Gaussian, median, and variance filters.",
    "The Gabor filter was created primarily to extract texture-based information.",
    "Based on the computation conducted during the Random Forest Classifier (RFC) model training, these returned characteristics were ranked in order of relevance."
  ],
